{"title":"访问苏联喜赋七言十首","authors":["李济深"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":2,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"访问苏联喜赋七言十首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李济深"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新华社讯　全国人民代表大会常务委员会副委员长李济深近作“访问苏联喜赋七言十首”，全文如下："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一知半解话苏联，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有感情怀意欲宣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天宝物华谈不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"休嫌陈说不周全。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五联邦合共和，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弟兄友爱一般过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盈亏无有通全力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设千般便利多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农专政此开端，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋斗艰难四十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"错误成功经验富，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教人由此得师传。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四十年华不少时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马列主义肇先知，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放之四海而皆准，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界都应认导师。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设卅年成就多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"较之资本国如何？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不徒数字资明证，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"科技迎头也赶过！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岂惟泱泱大国风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实行天下要为公，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国际主义崇高范，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"导向人群到大同。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"物丰地广世无俦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欧亚横跨两半球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万众一心齐努力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担当人类大谋猷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"魄力恢宏世所无，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凿山通海海通湖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从知世上无难事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只在人为大丈夫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国力充盈信有之，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国防有备更无疑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平胜利终谁属，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史车轮自告知。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真挚隆情与日深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情弥如海万千寻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中苏友好人人愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友谊长萦亿万心。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}